[00:00.000]--- Lesson 18  He often does this! 他经常干这种事
[00:04.467]After I had had lunch at a village pub, I looked for my bag.^我在一家乡村小酒店吃过午饭后，就找我的提包。
[00:10.971]I had left it on a chair beside the door and now it wasn't there!^我曾把它放在门边的椅子上，可这会儿不见了！
[00:16.980]As I was looking for it, the landlord came in.^当我正在寻找时，酒店老板走了进来。
[00:21.499]'Did you have a good meal?' he asked.^“您吃得好吗？”他问。
[00:25.130]'Yes, thank you,' I answered, 'but I can't pay the bill. I haven't got my bag.'^“很好，谢谢。”我回答，“但我付不了帐，我的提包没有了。”
[00:33.097]The landlord smiled and immediately went out.^酒店老板笑了笑，马上走了出去。
[00:37.616]In a few minutes he returned with my bag and gave it back to me.^一会儿工夫他拿着我的提包回来了，把它还给了我。
[00:43.572]'I'm very sorry,' he said. 'My dog had taken it into the garden. He often does this!'^“实在抱歉，”他说，“我的狗把它弄到花园里去了，他常干这种事！”
